Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.10,0:00:14.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Inherited will...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.64,0:00:17.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The tide of the times...\NPeople's dreams...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.54,0:00:20.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These things cannot be stopped.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.38,0:00:23.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As long as people seek\Nthe answer of freedom,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.48,0:00:26.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,these things will never cease to be!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.03,0:00:41.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I only believe in the future--\NI don't care if anyone laughs
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.20,0:00:46.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That racing passion makes you shine
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.54,0:00:52.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's too bright, but I want to gaze at it
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.54,0:00:56.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I sense "aesthetics" somewhere
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.15,0:00:59.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm really, really stuck on you
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.55,0:01:05.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I follow, follow in the footsteps\Nof a dream that resembles no one
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.99,0:01:09.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Until I dramatically get it
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.33,0:01:15.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Believe In Wonderland!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.14,0:01:24.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to catch, catch the shape\Nof a dream no one can see
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.44,0:01:30.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to go with you,\Nso passionate feelings
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.58,0:01:33.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't really need\Neverything to add up
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.59,0:01:36.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rather than run-of-the-mill daily life,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.76,0:01:40.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,run for paradise instead
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.36,0:01:45.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Believe In Wonderland!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.04,0:01:59.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah! My hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.38,0:02:00.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.98,0:02:03.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.99,0:02:09.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good! My hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.99,0:02:13.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.33,0:02:19.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow! So this is the scenery\Nthat the King of Pirates saw...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.33,0:02:21.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.00,0:02:26.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Finally... Finally the time\Nfor revenge has come.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.87,0:02:30.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just wait, you damn Straw Hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.34,0:02:36.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He finally showed up...\NTook him long enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.35,0:02:39.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please wait... Captain Smoker!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.68,0:02:42.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come with me, Tashigi.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.02,0:02:43.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.03,0:02:56.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Buggy's Revenge! The Man Who\NSmiles On The Execution Platform!"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.37,0:03:00.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, someone's on\Nthe execution platform!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.64,0:03:02.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who the heck is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.31,0:03:05.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That old man said\Nthat it was 22 years ago
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.98,0:03:09.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that the King of the Pirates died here...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.98,0:03:15.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey you over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.99,0:03:19.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come down right away!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.32,0:03:20.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.99,0:03:25.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a special execution platform\Nunder control of the World Government!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.33,0:03:28.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come down right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.00,0:03:33.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, you don't have\Nto be so strict, officer.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.00,0:03:36.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't come down,\NI'll just arrest you. I'm coming up now!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.34,0:03:43.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmph! Now's not\Nthe time for small fries.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.35,0:03:44.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.35,0:03:48.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been looking for you, Luffy.\NLong time no see...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.36,0:03:54.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.36,0:04:00.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me you forgot my face...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.63,0:04:03.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--How beautiful...\N--She's so pretty!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.30,0:04:04.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She is a woman of unrivaled beauty!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.97,0:04:07.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Her skin looks very smooth.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.97,0:04:12.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know anyone like you.\NWho the heck are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.64,0:04:18.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll never forget you...\Nbecause you're the first man who hit me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.32,0:04:20.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? I hit you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.32,0:04:27.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When your passionate\Nfist hit me that time...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.33,0:04:29.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gum-Gum...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.66,0:04:31.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pistol!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.00,0:04:41.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it felt good...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.01,0:04:51.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys... what's the most\Nbeautiful thing in the East Blue?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.02,0:04:53.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That'd be you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.69,0:04:55.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. It's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.69,0:05:00.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no man in this world that\Ndoesn't bow before my beauty.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.29,0:05:03.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I like strong men.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.96,0:05:08.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll make you mine, Luffy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.30,0:05:10.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up! No way!\NWho the heck are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.97,0:05:13.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You still haven't figured it out?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.64,0:05:17.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the police!\NHey, woman, come quietly!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.31,0:05:21.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're under arrest for\Nharming the police captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.31,0:05:24.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And you over there!\NGet off the execution platform!!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.32,0:05:27.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? Who'd you say you'd arrest?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.32,0:05:29.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.99,0:05:33.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you capable of that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.00,0:05:40.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A-Asst. Captain, this is a problem!\NShe's beautiful!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.67,0:05:43.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So what?! We'll arrest her!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.00,0:05:46.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's so beautiful\Nthat she's dazzling!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.00,0:05:48.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.34,0:05:50.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Terrorist bombing!!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.68,0:05:52.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's heading straight for her!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.68,0:05:57.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What the...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.02,0:05:59.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The fountain slipped!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.02,0:06:00.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What just happened?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.29,0:06:06.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was dangerous, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.29,0:06:12.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Flashily sorry. But your smooth skin\Nis unharmed, of course. So don't worry...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.96,0:06:16.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...beautiful lady Alvida.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.30,0:06:18.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Alvida?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.31,0:06:22.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't see Alvida.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.97,0:06:25.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Alvida! You blockhead!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.64,0:06:28.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really? You don't\Nlook like Alvida at all...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.32,0:06:35.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I changed after eating a devil fruit.\NThe name of the fruit is...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.65,0:06:37.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Smooth Smooth Fruit!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.99,0:06:42.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No attack can hurt my skin\Nbecause it slides off it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.99,0:06:48.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Unfortunately, my beauty\Ncouldn't be improved that much, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.00,0:06:52.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One big change was...\Nyes, my freckles are gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.34,0:06:54.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,N-No, that's not really what I meant.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.67,0:06:56.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After becoming a new person,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.44,0:07:01.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I joined forces with him since we\Nhad the same goal-- finding you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.29,0:07:13.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, the ultimate star\Nappears super flashily!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.96,0:07:15.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Monkey D. Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.93,0:07:21.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since the day you blew me off, I've\Nbeen obsessed with revenge on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.00,0:07:24.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That alone led me to finally find my crew.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.64,0:07:28.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was indeed a great adventure.\NI was missing parts of my body.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.97,0:07:34.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Laughs. Hell. Friendship. It was\Ntiny Buggy-kun's great adventure.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.31,0:07:35.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But Buggy-kun was...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.98,0:07:37.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why am I telling you\Na story, you bastard?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.98,0:07:40.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Well, what was your name?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.32,0:07:43.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Boggy? No, Boogie?\NNo, Behie... isn't right...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.99,0:07:46.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah! It's Buffoon!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.33,0:07:52.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Buffoon?! Stop messing around!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.16,0:07:55.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You sure haven't lost\Nyour nerve, you moron!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.67,0:07:58.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-It's Buggy the Clown!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.00,0:07:59.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,P-Pirates!!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.67,0:08:04.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the Buggy Pirates!!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.61,0:08:08.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,People! Remain flashily where you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.61,0:08:14.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll show you good how scary I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.95,0:08:17.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! It's Buggy!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.29,0:08:20.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You just remembered it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.96,0:08:24.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.30,0:08:29.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Long time no see, rubber man.\NIs Roronoa Zoro well, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.63,0:08:33.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, Cabaji. Good job.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.97,0:08:40.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To my several hundred billion\Nservants around the world! Look!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.31,0:08:44.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll now super flashily\Nstart the open execution!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.65,0:08:50.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Monkey D. Luffy! You can\Nno longer move even an inch.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.32,0:08:52.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You feel honored, Straw Hat?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.32,0:08:55.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can die in the same place\Nthe King of the Pirates died.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.61,0:09:10.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The atmospheric pressure\Nis dropping abnormally.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.27,0:09:13.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've never seen such\Na bizarre drop before.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.28,0:09:15.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that you mention it,\NI feel a strange wind...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.61,0:09:18.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A storm is coming... to this island!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.95,0:09:20.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A-A storm?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.62,0:09:23.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'd better hurry back to\Nthe ship or we'll be in trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.29,0:09:25.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Is it a pretty big one?\N--Hey...!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.29,0:09:27.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Hm?\N--Zoro!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.29,0:09:29.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you seen him?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.29,0:09:30.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You mean Luffy?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.29,0:09:32.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah... We got separated.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.63,0:09:36.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I also feel something strange...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.30,0:09:40.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...like... something terrible\Nis about to happen...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.64,0:09:45.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Pirates're here!\N--Pirates're here!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.98,0:09:49.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Pirates're here!\N--Run!\N--It's Buggy the Clown!!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.98,0:09:51.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.32,0:09:52.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Buggy the Clown!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.99,0:09:59.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.66,0:10:05.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes! In addition to Straw Hat Luffy,\NBuggy the Clown and Iron Club Alvida,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.63,0:10:12.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,all notorious pirates in the East Blue,\Nare taking over the square!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.00,0:10:15.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right under my nose...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.34,0:10:17.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What impudent jerks...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.68,0:10:21.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What should we do,\NCaptain Smoker?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.35,0:10:23.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Send Unit #1 to the sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.68,0:10:26.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Unit #2 is to secretly surround\Nthe square from the streets.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.35,0:10:30.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And have the rest stand by within\Nshooting range of the square.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.02,0:10:32.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--That's all.\N--Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.69,0:10:35.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Give this order to Unit #1.\N--Yes, sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.36,0:10:38.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Crush any pirate ships\Nas soon as they see them.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.36,0:10:43.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't let any pirates off of\Nthis island. Not even one pirate."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.04,0:10:52.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--An execution!\N--An execution will start!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.04,0:10:55.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Buggy the Clown will be\Nexecuting Straw Hat Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.71,0:10:57.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy's gonna be executed?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.72,0:10:59.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.38,0:11:00.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.32,0:11:04.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Take care of this!\N--Ahh... Ahh... Ahhhhh...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.66,0:11:07.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--S-S-S-Sanji!\N--Treat it like a lady! Got that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.99,0:11:10.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Oops! Ahhh...\N--We have to hurry, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.33,0:11:12.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Hey, Nami!\NWhere're we going?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.66,0:11:15.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The harbor, of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.00,0:11:17.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Harbor? Oh yeah, of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.34,0:11:21.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain Smoker!\NPlease come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.01,0:11:24.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Things are getting weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.01,0:11:27.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm? Wha...! Th-That kid...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.68,0:11:29.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's he doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.35,0:11:35.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Monkey D. Luffy. This can't be!\NLooks like he's about to be killed!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.69,0:11:38.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How pathetic that kid looks!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.02,0:11:44.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to see the place where\Nthe King of the Pirates died!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.36,0:11:46.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.36,0:11:50.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was somehow\Ndifferent from the others.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.03,0:11:53.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He caught my attention...\NSo I thought, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.37,0:11:57.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Does this mean that he's just\Nanother pirate after all?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.71,0:11:59.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain, are we\Nswooping in right away?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.71,0:12:01.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Idiot. Don't be hasty.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.31,0:12:03.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But if we don't hurry...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.65,0:12:06.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the one in command here!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.65,0:12:08.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.65,0:12:12.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A pirate is about\Nto kill another pirate.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.09,0:12:14.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is great.\NThey're saving us the trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.66,0:12:18.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen! Once that\NStraw Hat's head falls,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.50,0:12:22.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,surround Buggy,\NAlvida and their gangs!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.00,0:12:24.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't give them time to think!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.34,0:12:38.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pirate Monkey D. Luffy, the criminal,\Nis to be flashily executed for the crime
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.32,0:12:40.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,of getting me angry\Nby becoming stuck up!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.35,0:12:44.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Live it up flashily!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.36,0:12:50.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is my first time\Nseeing an execution.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.70,0:12:53.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're executing you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.03,0:12:54.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.70,0:12:56.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! Stop joking!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.37,0:12:58.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You stop joking!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.70,0:13:00.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Take this board off!! You bastard!!\N--Okay! We are now going
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.64,0:13:04.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Take it off!! You liar!\NYou jerkwad! You stupid head!\N--to start the flashy execution openly!!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.98,0:13:09.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ahhh!! Stop it!\NAhhh! I don't wanna die!!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.33,0:13:28.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I saw a big cumulus\Ncloud in the eastern sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.33,0:13:33.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A storm is coming.\NAn unimaginably big storm is...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.67,0:13:38.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If Buggy, Luffy and the others\Ngo crazy, the Navy will come out.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.01,0:13:41.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're done for if the ship is washed out\Nto sea when we have to get out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.35,0:13:43.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. That really is a big deal!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.35,0:13:47.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Navy may have\Nalready started taking action.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.69,0:13:51.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Going Merry is in danger!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.02,0:13:55.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-The Going Merry\Nwill be in the Navy's hands?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.36,0:13:58.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey, Nami! Hurry up!!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.03,0:13:59.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.97,0:14:06.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry to the harbor!\NCrush every single pirate ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.64,0:14:08.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.98,0:14:18.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Riding around on the Richie bike!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.98,0:14:24.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's that man?\NWho? Who? Who's that man?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.99,0:14:27.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.66,0:14:31.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So this is the rubber guy's ship...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.33,0:14:36.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He now has a bigger ship,\Nas if he's become a real pirate.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.00,0:14:40.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's about time for him to get\Nflashily executed by Captain Buggy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.01,0:14:48.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However...! Just in case the rubber guy,\Nwho has no chance of escaping,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.25,0:14:52.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,happens to escape,\Nburning this ship is... our job.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.69,0:15:02.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry. I won't do it again.\NPlease save me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.63,0:15:04.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why would I save you, idiot?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.63,0:15:07.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmph! This is what happens\Nwhen someone goes against us.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.97,0:15:11.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess this is it for\Nthe man I had my eye on...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.97,0:15:15.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since you have a big audience,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.27,0:15:18.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,do you wanna say\Nsomething before you die?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.31,0:15:23.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, that's okay. Whether you\Nwanna say something or not
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.61,0:15:26.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,doesn't matter since you're gonna die.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.99,0:15:33.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the man who'll be\NKing of the Pirates!!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.01,0:15:49.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wha...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.67,0:15:52.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,K-King of the Pirates, he said?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.68,0:15:55.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In this town, of all places...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.01,0:15:58.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a crazy thing to say...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.35,0:16:02.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well then, I guess I'll do it now...\Nyou damn piece of rubber.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.96,0:16:08.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Stop...\N--Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.29,0:16:10.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--...the execution!\N--Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.63,0:16:15.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Zoro! Sanji!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.97,0:16:18.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Zoro?!\N--Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.97,0:16:22.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shame on you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.37,0:16:25.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a limit to how much\Nyou can fool around, Luffy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.64,0:16:29.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're starting a sideshow,\Nlet me join you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.98,0:16:33.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What we have to do for now is\Ndrive those damn pirates away?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.98,0:16:39.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,P-Pirate hunter Zoro!!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.32,0:16:41.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sanji! Zoro!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.29,0:16:46.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you're here, Zoro!\NBut you are a little too late!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.66,0:16:49.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--We'll bring down...\N--...that execution platform!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.67,0:16:51.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Roronoa Zoro...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.67,0:16:56.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Guys... get them!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.01,0:16:57.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll get them!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.68,0:16:59.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big Sis Alvida!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.95,0:17:05.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Out of our way!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.96,0:17:15.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not even Zoro can stop me now!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.96,0:17:20.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the end of your captain!!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.30,0:17:22.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.64,0:17:28.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I cut down the execution platform...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.97,0:17:33.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen. The moment Monkey D. Luffy's\Nhead falls, we'll attack all together.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.31,0:17:38.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All units. Get ready for battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.32,0:17:39.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.66,0:17:46.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Zoro! Sanji!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.99,0:17:48.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Hurry up!\N--Usopp!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.53,0:17:50.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Nami!\N--This is heavy!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.66,0:17:55.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry. I'm... dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.67,0:17:59.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Idi...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.67,0:18:01.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't say something so stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.61,0:18:03.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He smiled!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.28,0:19:16.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm still alive after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.61,0:19:18.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I got lucky.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.62,0:19:26.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--H-Hey, do you believe in god?\N--Phew, lucky me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.62,0:19:30.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Stop talking nonsense.\NLet's get out of this town already!\N--I was worried what was going happen for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.29,0:19:32.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Another trouble seems to be brewing.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.30,0:19:39.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now! Corner those pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.97,0:19:43.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.64,0:19:45.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Here they come!\N--Tsk!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.32,0:19:55.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing! Amazing!\NIt's somehow gotten crazy!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.39,0:19:57.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing! Ahh! Amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.66,0:19:58.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.32,0:20:00.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ahhh... Z-Zoro!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.66,0:20:03.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is no time to be excited!\NWe need to get out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.33,0:20:05.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'd better hurry back to the ship
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.13,0:20:07.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,or we'll never be able\Nto leave the island.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.67,0:20:09.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We won't be able to\Nenter the Grand Line!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.50,0:20:12.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! That's not good!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.34,0:20:15.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Straw Hat gang is running away!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.34,0:20:18.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Capture them!\N--Go after them!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.35,0:20:25.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did he smile?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.35,0:20:28.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did he know he'd be saved?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.69,0:20:35.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No. At that moment, he seriously\Nthought his life was going to end there.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.03,0:20:39.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He accepted death and smiled\Nafter preparing himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.36,0:20:41.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain, please go seize the pirates.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.37,0:20:49.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey... have you seen any pirates\Nwho smiled on the execution platform?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.04,0:20:54.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,N-No way! Even if it's\Na brave-acting big shot,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.95,0:20:58.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,at the moment of death,\Nhe turns pale and dies in despair.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.05,0:21:02.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That straw hat man smiled...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.65,0:21:06.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...just like Gold Roger,\NKing of the Pirates,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.46,0:21:12.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,smiled 22 years ago in this town...\Non that execution platform...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.67,0:21:24.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.01,0:21:26.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where did that Straw Hat go?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.01,0:21:29.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir. He's running towards the sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.68,0:21:35.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's Unit #1 doing? They should've\Nblown up their ship by now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.02,0:21:38.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well... They're back for\Nrefitting because they couldn't
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.99,0:21:41.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,light the powder\Ndue to the sudden rain...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.36,0:21:43.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.19,0:21:47.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A reserve unit is currently getting\Nready to attack the ship instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.36,0:21:54.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain Smoker! If we let them sail\Nout now, they'll enter the Grand Line!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.04,0:21:59.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The wind is blowing towards the west.\NIt's a tailwind for their ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.65,0:22:04.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are these all coincidences?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.98,0:22:11.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's as if heaven is trying\Nto let that man live.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.32,0:22:14.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--We'd better hurry\Nor we'll be in trouble!\N--We're gonna make it to the Grand Line like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.66,0:22:16.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am White Hunter Smoker.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.56,0:22:18.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On my honor as a\NNavy Headquarters Captain,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.60,0:22:21.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let that man\Nleave this island!!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.35,0:22:46.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wind, blow!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.02,0:22:49.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The storm of fate has arrived!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.79,0:22:51.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.79,0:22:53.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.07,0:23:01.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My overflowing feelings don't connect
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.07,0:23:05.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,as I firmly squeeze your hand back
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.98,0:23:10.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll set off by myself,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.91,0:23:16.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so keep watching me intently\Nas I go into the distance
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.76,0:23:25.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was thinking about it\Na bit since this morning
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.76,0:23:30.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why is it so hot?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.33,0:23:40.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Starting from some point, I haven't\Nbeen able to get away from that
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.81,0:23:46.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to catch those\Nfeelings that rushed off,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.68,0:23:51.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and I'm already about\Nto overtake myself, even
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.56,0:23:56.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to embrace my\Ndreams that have jumped out
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.56,0:24:01.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With you, I can run there
